=== Stickers ===
''See also [[Stickers]] for more detailed information.''[[File:2-VaultCat.webp|thumb|100px|The "Vault Cat" sticker.]]'''Stickers''' in the inventory are images that users can upload and place in an [[Instances|instance]]. Stickers can be placed on almost any surface in a world for all users in the instance to see. Only one sticker may be placed by each user at a time, and stickers will automatically disappear when the user leaves the instance. Users with an active VRC+ subscription can upload up to 18 custom stickers.

=== Items ===
''See also [[Special:MyLanguage/Items|Items]] for more detailed information.''
[[File:THE_REFERENCE_CUBE_item_original.png|thumb|100px|A image of "THE REFERENCE CUBE" item.]]
'''Items''' are objects that users can spawn within a world. Items can take the place of toys, tools, gadgets, etc. World creators can disable items in their world if they wish.

